&#125;</code></pre>

  <h2>Workflow</h2>

  <ol>
    <li>Run <code>buoy show all</code> to get a full snapshot</li>
    <li>Use <code>buoy show drift -S high</code> to focus on critical issues</li>
    <li>Fix drift with <code>buoy fix</code>, then re-run to verify</li>
    <li>Track progress with <code>buoy show history</code></li>
  </ol>

